FBIS3-49902 "dreeu012_y_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 YUGOSLAVIA Kosovo Typhoid Fever Breaks Out From Polluted Water AU1801212294 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 GMT 18 Jan 94 AU1801212294 Tirana TVSH Television Network Language: Albanian Article Type:BFN [Text] Typhoid fever is now breaking out in several communes of the republic of Kosova, like the epidemics of jaundice and measles some time ago. Tests carried out by the Kosova Epidemiological Enterprise confirm that these diseases have appeared as a result of drinking polluted water. Reports state that in the Shtime commune some 20 people suffering from typhoid fever have sought medical advice.
